title: OnePlus 9 Pro and Nord N200 return to lowest-ever prices today
content:
The OnePlus 10 series is just around the corner, which means OnePlus has some old inventory it likely wants to clear out before the new phones arrive. The company discounted the OnePlus 9 series and the Nord N200 last month at decent prices, but now the OnePlus 9 Pro and Nord N200 have dropped even

The post OnePlus 9 Pro and Nord N200 return to lowest-ever prices today appeared first on xda-developers.
description: This latest OnePlus deal bring the OnePlus 9 Pro down to $799, and the Nord N200 is available for just $209.
